# Runtime and tool outputs
**/_runtime/
**/work/
**/transcript
**/*.wlf
**/*.vcd
**/*.fst
**/*.log
**/*.jou
**/*.pb
**/*.rpt.tmp
*.statebak

# Local project instances are not published from this platform repository.
projects/*/
!projects/
!projects/README.md
!projects/.gitkeep
config/projects/*/
!config/projects/
!config/projects/README.md

# Project-local memory that should stay outside permanent history.
projects/*/memory/transient/**
projects/*/memory/**/transient/**
projects/*/_archive/memory_history/**

# Local/vendor source documents and parser extracts.
# Review source-document redistribution rights before publishing these.
projects/*/00_SPEC/raw_docs/*.pdf
projects/*/01_DocParse/mineru_raw/**
!projects/*/01_DocParse/mineru_raw/
!projects/*/01_DocParse/mineru_raw/.gitkeep

# Python/tool cache
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.pytest_cache/

# Local generated library database and large uploaded source files.
library/.local/
library/files/**/*.pdf
library/files/**/*.zip
library/files/**/*.tar
library/files/**/*.tar.gz
library/files/**/*.7z
library/files/fpga_io_tables/**/*.xlsx
library/files/fpga_io_tables/**/*.xls
library/files/fpga_io_tables/**/*.csv
library/files/fpga_io_tables/**/*.tsv
library/files/fpga_schematics/**/*.pdf
library/files/fpga_schematics/**/*.zip
library/parsed/**/images/
library/parsed/**/mineru_raw/
library/parsed/**/text_raw/
library/parsed/**/*.pdf
library/parsed/**/*.zip

# Local workflow runtime state
.omx/
.codex/skills/

# Local audit and migration notes
*_AUDIT.md
/archive/

# Local editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.tmp

